Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.56,0:00:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind feels so nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.94,0:00:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.61,0:02:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\2c&H0FFFFFF&\3c&H777777&\4c&HFFFFFF\i1\b1\fnSegoe Script\pos(1565,932)}CENTER OF THE WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this place a bit {\i1}too{\i0} cramped?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not much we can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.96,0:02:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did we even pick this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the other rooms were taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That studio we used last time wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That studio also costs a ton.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.01,0:02:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we really gonna be okay? The festival's right around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,arE wE reAlLY gOnNA be oKaY? THe fEsTivAl's rIGhT ARoUnd tHE cOrNeR.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we stop wasting time then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we good on this part or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I should start where you told me before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to give you a signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do we really need that last part?\N- I was wondering about that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer keeping it as is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I think both of them work, so let's have Momoka-san make the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be a bit too loud since we all start playing at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how it sounds without my guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:02:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,From the last chorus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pooped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, Burton Sister's gonna play right at the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.39,0:03:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not really…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They {\i1}are{\i0} pretty hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.48,0:03:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, our name's there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, duh. We're performing too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We're up on the first day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, we'll be the first ones on our stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means we should be able watch the last performers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And that one, and that one too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you even make it to all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We get a free pass, might as well make the most of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How big is the audience gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a festival, so it depends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The bigger stages will probably be packed during peak hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't know about the smaller ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's where we're supposed to leave our mark, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- Actually-\N- Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard they changed your performance time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be rootin' for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We might actually be playing on the second day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently one of the bands had to cancel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll still be on the same stage, but I asked for their time slot instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The second day's supposed to be an all-nighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a serious upgrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So everyone's fine with the change?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Could luck really be on our side this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you guys have some time after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, isn't that…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we might as well do some recon ahead of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we really playing in this huge place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- Nope. That's the main stage.\N- Main?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be on the small stage over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, there's more than one stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You really haven't done your homework, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:05:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The popular bands play on the big one,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and upstarts like us go on the small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.22,0:05:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, Diamond Dust are on the big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all so...cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be challenging Diamond Dust, who are up there on the big stage
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,from our tiny little stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like in {\i1}Giant Killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A cornered rat will even bite a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither them nor the fans think of it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But we do. Momoka-san and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all sure you're on board with the schedule change?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.76,0:05:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be nice, playing under a sky like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please lend me a guitar for the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay, I'm off to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Weren't you working together?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We are, but Nina-san found a second job all on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if to call her selfish or just whimsical at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.07,0:06:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She made a decision. To make it on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,True. She's come a long way, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, can she actually play the guitar now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}FROM: TENDO AWA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz9.173\\pos(932,524)\\fscx100\fscy100}To Subaru-san. I hope you are doing well during the lingering summer heat. I assume your daily life is quite busy, but allow me to ask, how are things with your acting school? There is a new role for which auditions have started recently, and I would love it if you could take part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at her, being all sunshine and rainbows now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}LIAR
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru's still hiding it from her grandma, isn't she.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I like that side of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not like I actually care...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that one day, you can find it in you to forgive them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that'll happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You never know what the future holds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least they're within your reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You may not see or talk to them anymore, but they're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The people that were dear to me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,have turned to ashes by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do I make music?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmmm...probably because it allows me to connect with others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because it gives me somewhere I can be honest with myself, I guess.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's see…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because it lets me forget everything and feel free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:08:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}want to feel like I wasn't in the wrong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's when it really starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, and you are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're TogeToge. Togenashi Togeari.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, alright. You can park over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're up in the evening, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. So watch the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we have some time to see other bands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But today's our big day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but seeing other bands could help us get pumped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You better not be late though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I come with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No Ninas allowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this our dressing room?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}TOGENASHI TOGEARI
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You came!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is this a good time?\N- Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have given me a heads-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no fun, now is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:09:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it's no small thing playing on the second day at that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was mostly luck though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina-chan, how are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm great! Can't say the same for my guitar skills though...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a much better look on your face now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, looking like a real songstress now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you done with the yapping?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Introduce me, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Kyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Small world out there, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,For your information, she's a fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I love your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We should play together again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you’ll have me…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re up for it? Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a pic for the occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You good at funny faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,F-funny faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you guys come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Say cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice faces you got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ditching us wasn't very nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, we got a bunch of likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Can't wait to see TogeToge".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re finally getting noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They said it's all-you-can-drink here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We have different definitions of "a bit".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Miura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.22,0:10:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re Miura-san...right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the wrong person!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, huh? It wasn't her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- Bottoms up!\N- Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I just noticed Subaru's not back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She's probably still running between stages.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No fair, I wanted to go with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She's already back in the dressing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Put that down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}TOGENASHI TOGEARI
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it? Did you get to everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky. I wanted to go too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Jealous, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you, getting all perked up on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the first time I went to a festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,a drummer said something that stuck with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That as a drummer, he could always see his bandmates' back and support them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, it really resonated with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw myself in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru-chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent a message to my grandma yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That I want to do something other than acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So yeah, let's keep this band going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:11:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we mess up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the kind of stubborn girl who always does her own thing and runs on ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're shy, and not exactly friendly on top of that. Of course you'd get bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're always honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And you always give it your all, so I can trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see where you'll take us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm lying though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see when we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s really huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it is called the {\i1}main{\i0} stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot more people now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo-chan, can you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, and I hate this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to lift you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you picked up the habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This song…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you all for coming here today!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For those who don’t know us yet, we are…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Diamond Dust!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stay with us until the end please!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you ever going to stop playing the tragic heroine?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You were wrong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no point in keeping this up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You must really be an idiot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shut up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the edge of the world where everything begins{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only doubt dances{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Boredom only accelerates{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Living in an unfinished dream{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I laugh, completely cornered{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ready to unleash myself to support your sharp gaze{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it will never be enough{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those who lack the courage to shout often reap all the laurels{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A prayer for those who have changed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will continue to scream again and again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:15:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even a prisoner of the chains of a cruel destiny{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a different cycle of desperate sadness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Welcome, everyone!\N- Those in the back, we see you guys too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They actually got better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,When they revealed an idol as their new singer,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,they got a lot of flak for becoming industrialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't look down on us, we'll show you what we're made of!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're putting that frustration into a driving force.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And the fans are feeling it at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So they {\i1}did{\i0} think of it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider me pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I really love this kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san. Everyone. Let's steal every single one of these fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Togenashi Togeari, sound check please!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alright, starting with the drums then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alright, we're good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Say something into the microphone please.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Great, thank you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! We'll be in your care!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alright, now the bass please.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Great. Will you be using pedals?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, for distortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Done, anything else?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost our turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just to get us perked up-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, where's Miura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}NEW TANTANMEN RAMEN
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She sent me a message a while ago. Said she'll be in the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't even visit us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I like that she keeps her distance. Makes her feel more professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure that's her reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Togenashi Togeari, you're up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, wanna huddle up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ew, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to...raise our pinkies?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Before us is the most important concert of our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, you have to sing your lungs out so that everyone can hear you. Scream if you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Rip their hearts out with our song.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you made her cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a grip already, we're up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't play the guitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now {\i1}that's{\i0} rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well… nice to meet you. We're Togenashi Togeari.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're a band.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And uh, well, it's not easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all cowards, we don't trust people, we always hesitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, we even rope each other into something and then don't take it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, is that supposed to be about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Who exactly are you calling indecisive?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not wrong, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were our guitarist Momoka-san and our keyboardist Tomo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is our monstrously self-righteous vocalist, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally our bassist, Rupa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Infighting is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And on drums, we have…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"Give it up. It'll never happen."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's impossible. Be realistic."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:19:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Consider yourself lucky."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's hard for me too."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how reality tried to drown me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,with a disgusting toxic smile on its face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Through this song, I'll stay true to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Through this song, I'll make everyone who didn't believe in me change their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,At all those who denied everything that I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.68,0:20:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to shout that I was right all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter how much I get, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H0A0A0B&\3c&H0C0DDA&}Dore dake te ni iretemo {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter how much I make mine,\NI can't keep up, can't keep up, can't keep up,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H0A0A0B&\3c&H0C0DDA&}Dore dake jibun no mono ni shitemo shitemo shitemo {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm never good enough{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H0A0A0B&\3c&H0C0DDA&}Oitsukenai na{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dreaming too big, they say those rotten words{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H0A0A0B&\3c&H0C0DDA&}Takanozomi shishugi nante kusatta youna kotoba{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never wanted to be above everyone else{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H0A0A0B&\3c&H0C0DDA&}Dareshimo dare yori mo sugurete hoshiku wa nai nda yo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's only one reason{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H0A0A0B&\3c&H0C0DDA&}Riyuu wa tada hitotsu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:21:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To shatter this void, not to be the best.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:21:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H0A0A0B&\3c&H0C0DDA&}Uchikudaitete hoshii kara kono kuukyo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I could look at things with a pure heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H0A0A0B&\3c&H0C0DDA&}Junsuina kokoro de mireta koro wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything seemed like a rainbow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H0A0A0B&\3c&H0C0DDA&}Subete ga nijiiro ni mieru soutei{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But even the things I've always wanted to grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H0A0A0B&\3c&H0C0DDA&}Tsukamitai mono sura boyakete nijinde iku no sa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Become a blur and disappear now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to die, I want to live so much it hurts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1\c&H0A0A0B&\3c&H0C0DDA&}Shinitai tte omotte nakute shinu hodo ikite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This soul of mine, this soul of mine{\i0}
